{
  "openapi": "3.1.0",
  "info": {
    "title": "事务管理示例",
    "description": "演示事务管理、并发控制和回滚",
    "version": "4.0.0"
  },
  "paths": {
    "/transfer": {
      "post": {
        "summary": "Transfer",
        "description": "转账 (演示事务)\n\n══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════\nACID 特性演示\n══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════\nA - Atomicity (原子性):\n    扣钱和加钱要么都成功，要么都失败\n\nC - Consistency (一致性):\n    转账前后总金额不变\n\nI - Isolation (隔离性):\n    并发转账互不影响\n\nD - Durability (持久性):\n    提交后永久保存\n══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════",
        "operationId": "transfer_transfer_post",
        "requestBody": {
          "content": {
            "application/json": {
              "schema": {
                "$ref": "#/components/schemas/TransferRequest"
              }
            }
          },
          "required": true
        },
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "Successful Response",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {}
              }
            }
          },
          "422": {
            "description": "Validation Error",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "$ref": "#/components/schemas/HTTPValidationError"
                }
              }
            }
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "/orders": {
      "post": {
        "summary": "Create Order Endpoint",
        "description": "创建订单 (演示复杂事务)\n\n事务操作:\n1. 查询产品\n2. 检查库存\n3. 扣减库存\n4. 创建订单\n全部成功或全部失败！",
        "operationId": "create_order_endpoint_orders_post",
        "requestBody": {
          "content": {
            "application/json": {
              "schema": {
                "$ref": "#/components/schemas/OrderCreate"
              }
            }
          },
          "required": true
        },
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "Successful Response",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {}
              }
            }
          },
          "422": {
            "description": "Validation Error",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "$ref": "#/components/schemas/HTTPValidationError"
                }
              }
            }
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "/orders/safe": {
      "post": {
        "summary": "Create Order Safe Endpoint",
        "description": "创建订单 (演示并发控制)\n\n使用悲观锁防止并发问题:\n- with_for_update() 锁定产品行\n- 其他事务必须等待",
        "operationId": "create_order_safe_endpoint_orders_safe_post",
        "requestBody": {
          "content": {
            "application/json": {
              "schema": {
                "$ref": "#/components/schemas/OrderCreate"
              }
            }
          },
          "required": true
        },
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "Successful Response",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {}
              }
            }
          },
          "422": {
            "description": "Validation Error",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "$ref": "#/components/schemas/HTTPValidationError"
                }
              }
            }
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "/accounts": {
      "get": {
        "summary": "List Accounts",
        "description": "查看所有账户余额",
        "operationId": "list_accounts_accounts_get",
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "Successful Response",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {}
              }
            }
          }
        }
